rows.label: tev032701_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Bihabba about humans.

rows.label: tev032701_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Bihabba about recent developments.

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0001
rows.name:
We've been around numerous galaxies, but this is the
first time we've met anything like you, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0002
rows.name:
You're all made of machines, right?! And you make all
this this weird food! And your clothes are so...
Well, it's all just very very unfamiliar, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0003
rows.name:
Anyway, we're going to enjoy studying a pack of
walking, talking mysteries like you, won't we?
I hope you enjoy it as well, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0008
rows.name:
We Ma-non are busting out our skills to help you guys
out here on on Mira, aren't we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0009
rows.name:
We even started that Candid & Credible operation to
supply you with weapons, did we not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0010
rows.name:
And some folks like Heradot are fixing up the ship so
we can head back into space when the time is right,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0011
rows.name:
...What, me? Oh, I'm not as handy with machines as
other Ma-non, so I'm sort of keeping an eye on them.
Just to make sure no one gets hurt, you understand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0016
rows.name:
Oh, you found a Skell that the Ganglion were trying
to to get their grubby claws on? That's great![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0017
rows.name:
If they were trying that hard to get it despite already
having so many dangerous Skells to begin with,
then the writing's on the wall, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0018
rows.name:
That thing is clearly bad news, wouldn't you say?
Probably worse than we even know...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0019
rows.name:
Anyway, maybe think twice before you get in there and
start tinkering with it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0025
rows.name:
Wouldn't you agree that Skell is a nightmare waiting to
happen? It wouldn't surprise me if it's powerful enough
to obliterate the whole planet...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0026
rows.name:
I mean, it's the Ganglion's, right? And just look what
they did to get it back. I don't think you spend that
much effort unless it's for something really important.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0027
rows.name:
It's gone now, but we need to be ready for whatever
horrible surprise that thing is holding in store for us,
wouldn't you agree?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0035
rows.name:
Did the Ganglion really get one of your own people to
double-cross you? We've been in a a panic since we
first heard the news.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0036
rows.name:
If they got one human to do it, then someone could
likely just march in here and blow up our ship,
couldn't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0037
rows.name:
It's bad enough that some Ma-non are proposing we
bar all humans from entering the ship, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0038
rows.name:
Anyway, things are pretty chaotic on the ship now,
so I hope we do something really soon...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0045
rows.name:
At least that Zu Pharg monstrosity is out of the
picture, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0046
rows.name:
But still, the Ganglion are going to pull out all the stops
now that the endgame is approaching, aren't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0047
rows.name:
Don't forget that they've still got that mysterious Skell
they stole, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG0048
rows.name:
Anyway, you'll need to be super extra careful out there,
I imagine? Now go get those real bodies of yours and
come back safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1001
rows.name:
You've taken care of the Ganglion, and we've mostly
wrapped up repairs to to our ship...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1002
rows.name:
We also all had a talk, and I think we're all getting
ready to to to head back out to space, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1003
rows.name:
...What's that? Come back soon?
You're going to miss us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1004
rows.name:
Well, uh... Don't worry, I suppose? We'll head back to
to New LA just as soon as we finish our research
expedition, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1005
rows.name:
I mean, you've basically changed the fate of our race
by making us hopeless pizza addicts, so who knows
what will happen if we don't return?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1010
rows.name:
Now that we don't have to worry about death from
above, Heradot decided to enjoy a pizza up on top
of the ship, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1011
rows.name:
Everything was going great until she dropped her last
slice of pepperoni. But then...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1012
rows.name:
Well, then she took a flying leap right off the ship to
try and catch it! Can you imagine?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1013
rows.name:
I thought she was done for, but she nabbed the slice in
midair, did a double somersault, and and splashed
down in the water safe and sound! That's good, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev032701_MSG1014
rows.name: Talk about amazing reflexes, am I right?[ST:wait ]
